flowchart TD
  U[User] --> A[Agent Runtime
(Claude Code / other MCP client)]

  A -->|Tool call| H[Hook layer
(PreToolUse/PostToolUse)]
  H --> G[MCP Context Gateway
(Context Mode-style)]

  subgraph Sandbox[Sandboxed execution]
    G -->|ctx_execute / ctx_batch_execute| P[Isolated subprocess
(per-call)]
    P --> FS[(Artifacts on disk
logs, snapshots, API payloads)]
    P -->|stdout only| G
  end

  subgraph Memory[Local persistence + retrieval]
    G --> DB[(SQLite)]
    DB --> FTS[(FTS5 index)]
    G -->|ctx_index / ctx_fetch_and_index| FTS
    A -->|ctx_search| G
    G -->|BM25-ranked exact snippets| A
  end

  A -->|Compact response| U
